{"tid":1027166,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《美國隊長》 4K UHD 藍光碟最快於本月底開賣","createTime":"2019-02-18T15:33:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T15:33:04.000Z","uid":105567,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8b90d1607577f49feb742bcdef21739ac5f69d66","tid":1027166,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T15:33:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://post76.hk/news/2019/02/captain-america-4k-mcu/?from=forum_bottom_new\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpost76.hk%2Fnews%2F2019%2F02%2Fcaptain-america-4k-mcu%2F%3Ffrom%3Dforum_bottom_new&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpEjw60zqfRdeCYg0zJNkavsY%3D&h=0f8a7634\" target=\"_blank\">https://post76.hk/news/2019/02/captain-america-4k-mcu/?from=forum_bottom_new</a><br />\n<br />\n相信有不少《復仇者聯盟》系列或 MCU (Marvel Cinematic Universe) 的粉絲已把握好農曆年假期，搶先開始重溫過去十年近 20 部經典作品。然而聲畫要求極高玩家都必定會發現當下由 Disney 發行的附設中文字幕 MCU 作品只有《銀河守護隊2》、《復仇者聯盟》三部曲、《黑豹》、《雷神奇俠3》、《蟻俠2》，而 SONY 及 Universal 則各得《蜘蛛俠:强勢回歸》及《新變形俠醫》&hellip; 屈指一算其實不超過十套作品。有留意外國影碟資訊的玩家相信都知美加地區最快將於本月底推出《美國隊長1》，更有傳第二及第三集或將於 4 月底，承《復仇者聯盟4》上映之勢推出。根據目前 <a href=\"http://bluray.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbluray.com&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpEjw60zqfRdeCYg0zJNkavsY%3D&h=fbbc87fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bluray.com</a> 資料所見，最先開賣《美國隊長1》4K 的地區很大機會是加拿大，緊隨其後的地區將會是法國等歐洲地區&hellip; 至於最新消息指美版《美國隊長1》4K 的推出日期有機會順延至 4 月《復4》上映期間&hellip; 大家密切留意出碟日期變化啦&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://post76.hk/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/CA1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpost76.hk%2Fnews%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2FCA1.jpg&h=9b5c4416&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://post76.hk/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/f5948ac9-0189-4914-acea-525c82caee19_1.1ac3ec32829baf65f2f3b73928790770.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpost76.hk%2Fnews%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2Ff5948ac9-0189-4914-acea-525c82caee19_1.1ac3ec32829baf65f2f3b73928790770.jpeg&h=9168991b&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}